<li class='cover' id='bookCover_232577'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/232577.Gorillas_in_the_Mist"><img alt="Gorillas in the Mist" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1629496426l/232577._SX98_.jpg" />
